        </article>

        <article class="skillcard research">
          <h3>Research & Development</h3>
          <p>
            Vulnerability research & exploit analysis • Reversing & malware analysis (developing) •
            Exploit prototyping & PoCs • Lightweight tooling/automation • Applied cryptography •
            Exploring AI/ML & blockchain security
